---
title: Blogs
layout: 'base.njk'
description: I blog about web design, development, deployment, and interesting aspects of daily life. My monthly 'Learning Log' captures articles I'm reading and things I'm learning.
---

<div class="blog-title">
  <h1>
    <img src="/assets/favicon/blog.svg" alt="favicon">
      &nbsp;{{ title }}</h1>
    <p>{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
  {% include 'blog-list.njk' %}
  <hr>
    <!-- categories list -->
    <div class="categories">
      <h3>Categories:</h3>
      <ul>
        {% for category in collections.categories %}
          <li>
            <a href="/blog/{{ category.slug }}">{{ category.title | capitalize }}</a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>